18 #ifndef __G_PATTERN_H__
19 #define __G_PATTERN_H__
20 
21 #if !defined (__GLIB_H_INSIDE__) && !defined (GLIB_COMPILATION)
22 #error "Only <glib.h> can be included directly."
23 #endif
24 
25 #include <glib/gtypes.h>
26 
27 G_BEGIN_DECLS
28 
29 
30 typedef struct _GPatternSpec    GPatternSpec;
31 
32 GLIB_AVAILABLE_IN_ALL
33 GPatternSpec* g_pattern_spec_new       (const gchar  *pattern);
34 GLIB_AVAILABLE_IN_ALL
35 void          g_pattern_spec_free      (GPatternSpec *pspec);
36 GLIB_AVAILABLE_IN_ALL
37 gboolean      g_pattern_spec_equal     (GPatternSpec *pspec1,
38                     GPatternSpec *pspec2);
39 GLIB_AVAILABLE_IN_ALL
40 gboolean      g_pattern_match          (GPatternSpec *pspec,
41                     guint         string_length,
42                     const gchar  *string,
43                     const gchar  *string_reversed);
44 GLIB_AVAILABLE_IN_ALL
45 gboolean      g_pattern_match_string   (GPatternSpec *pspec,
46                     const gchar  *string);
47 GLIB_AVAILABLE_IN_ALL
48 gboolean      g_pattern_match_simple   (const gchar  *pattern,
49                     const gchar  *string);
50 
51 G_END_DECLS
52 
53 #endif /* __G_PATTERN_H__ */
